{"tid":871358,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"歧視中國人？2中國客行李中有藏羚毛披肩 遭印度逮捕","createTime":"2018-10-22T01:00:42.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-22T01:57:02.000Z","uid":184679,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"acdbbac0e2d25522ddfcea04f762417b3df2cd81","tid":871358,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-22T01:00:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://newsstatic.rthk.hk/images/mfile_1424079_1_20181022011744.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnewsstatic.rthk.hk%2Fimages%2Fmfile_1424079_1_20181022011744.jpg&h=7041eff4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n兩名中國女性因涉嫌「走私」沙圖什(Shahtoosh)披肩，18日在印度德里機場被捕。<br />\n<br />\n環球網引述印度論壇報報導，印度官方聲明稱，兩名中國女性18日在即將登上從德里飛往上海的航班時，遭海關從行李中搜出15條沙圖什披肩，隨後二人被逮。<br />\n<br />\n沙圖什披肩由藏羚羊毛製成，被嚴格禁止進行國際交易。報導稱，這些披肩的市場估價約為45萬盧比（約6135萬美元）。<br />\n<br />\n接手該案件的蘭迪律師事務所管理委員會主任劉逸星表示，目前印度海關以違反相關法律規定為由，追究兩人的刑事責任：首先罰款45萬人民幣（約6.5萬美元），其次要羈押她們，可能會被判處3到7年的有期徒刑。<br />\n<br />\n劉逸星表示，機場每天有大量的其他國家的遊客攜帶同樣的產品出境，印度海關心知肚明，但不對這些人進行查處或者處罰。而在碰到中國人時，他們往往帶有民族偏見，會處罰中國人，該案充分體現出印度海關在對待中國人時的嚴重執法不公和帶有的歧視性。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://udn.com/news/story/7331/3434144\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fudn.com%2Fnews%2Fstory%2F7331%2F3434144&d=RLcLEq4rWdBVigYxFuaZEjM0pwszV1jUpWwTgNsMWwc%3D&h=405df97a\" target=\"_blank\">https://udn.com/news/story/7331/3434144</a>"},{"pid":"8146b8205f5e62f39840cf164a263793cdeee0fa","tid":871358,"uid":108347,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-22T01:03:43.000Z","msg":"犯咩法比人拉都係歧視，因為一定有其他國家嘅人犯左法走得甩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"49c07ceb8a3c551bc5863185572b68fd4b9e5d14","tid":871358,"uid":84128,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-22T01:04:10.000Z","msg":"自己做錯野<br />\n又話歧視中國人<br />\n千錯萬錯<br />\n都係人地歧視中國人既錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e0a8534b62c75efe04d02760eceda6fe321fac6f","tid":871358,"uid":62532,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-22T01:05:21.000Z","msg":"45萬盧比 = 6000 美金喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1df842308b5a14861da28417fb012a832d7d2e96","tid":871358,"uid":166785,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-22T01:22:16.000Z","msg":"仲唔送入去印度獄，一日奸佢十次八次"},{"pid":"0b76a303be79a3ae65c34eb81e0ba3acb823236d","tid":871358,"uid":52881,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-22T01:23:53.000Z","msg":"45萬盧比（約6135萬美元）<br />\n<br />\n印度盧布幾時變到咁值錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b0955cb4ca1307d1d63ea55bf32cbfe9975f0c4f","tid":871358,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"0b76a303be79a3ae65c34eb81e0ba3acb823236d","tid":871358,"uid":52881,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-22T01:23:53.000Z","msg":"45萬盧比（約6135萬美元）<br />\n<br />\n印度盧布幾時變到咁值錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-22T01:54:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b4426a134619c038d12d33e77c399ad54304c92","tid":871358,"uid":130595,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-22T01:57:02.000Z","msg":"仲諗住係乜驚天走私成 約6135萬美元 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n求其帶幾件披肩就差唔多5億港紙"}]}